  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f8b270f-e6db-44be-b2a3-4207dcee90eb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1237508d-c26f-4bcb-9e1d-8da476694c0d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dfdd4bb0-4338-4204-a13e-1483e9ab88bf\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 3</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a3b95c8e-8a58-4c3c-8f54-fd827a143733\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6d1d689c-43f5-46d8-9b01-0ce133ce1488\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7dc11e8d-9446-428a-812e-d5f43ed689db\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b385fe20-8ef0-4fb1-aba8-b1757fcb6657\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요청사항]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dd73c9df-ab96-4f20-b240-07e523817115\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ab18bbff-5ee9-4e99-bc22-e45e7a21a019\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>여기에 나오는 첨부파일이나 자료는 오로지 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 작업에 의해 만들어진 문서들입니다. 이 작업은 마음껏 퍼가시되 다만, 좋아요 또는 댓글로 표시해 주시고 다운로드하여 주시기를 권장드립니다. 앞으로는 좋은 자료는 업로드하고 서로 소통하도록 하겠습니다. 물론 아는 범위에서 질문과 답볍도 환영입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a71a30d1-6a0e-4223-a9c8-f70d8444ba81\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-35b1a14c-30f7-492f-9f45-efe8abf9c295\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-965366c6-ed3e-494c-8c52-62cbabf1d069\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b158b2dc-2ef7-474b-93ab-f29ab920a214\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>여러분은 매출관리를 어떻게 하시나요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9d278b5a-eef7-4747-a309-0ec756b81db5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a86e4913-065b-492c-aee9-949d26da2a98\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66bd8e41-10f8-4ce8-806b-c8ad8a57410a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">인쇄에서 활용하는 문서는 여러가지가 있습니다. 제가 D회사 전산개발팀장으로 있을 때 문서를 관리하고 활용하는 부분에 대해 여러가지 고민을 했었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-23577b7b-8d9a-404d-ac7a-8cb43f3b2d97\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-42a1f872-73f1-45f2-806a-12f04cc4d242\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-68c2f752-a9d9-4509-af66-ca9a03f717bb\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1c5254fc-0f8f-4755-978e-f8f73fdaf246\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d9d8be8-c828-441f-ba2e-3cb4c38f520e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f539542b-86d5-40fe-a357-244fc808f5bd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-299ff9bd-f789-4067-a220-361b93f5b69a\" style=\"\">흩어져있으면  파일들이고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a77d61d3-972a-427b-ad30-021b3f306768\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f67614eb-6493-4a96-a6f5-5e96982dcb6c\" style=\"\">모아서 관리하면 데이터베이스다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bad89ec0-6265-4f2c-a4a9-f312d47e6f00\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ffecbe23-6af5-4d36-a9bd-fa603e5c36c7\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bacd9278-8f62-42e4-9df5-9c4d702db828\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">위의 말처럼 모든 자료는 관리가 안되면 그냥 하나의 파일이지만 이것을 특정 장소에 보관하고 쉽게 찾고 활용하면 그것은 데이터로서의 제기능을 한다고 생각합니다. 그런 취지에서 저는 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 견적서 파일을 하나 올려봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4dc6373d-b224-4090-9c41-9c6c6dca5096\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-30bac902-d4bc-41f1-9189-f64210cd2fa8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-21bac2ef-c6da-45a0-a8bd-58f5fd451899\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dabaaf4a-0b88-4795-994b-0b15c78afcb1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-475544b5-c3ef-4407-a0aa-920bdcc31e78\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3b70ea7-10fb-4584-a31a-46db8edffbf4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ec029888-a0dd-4e13-bab0-47d2f305df9c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니 견적서 양식</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-file se-l-default\" id=\"SE-255ec6c7-293d-4448-82bd-f97a2d608b58\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-file se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-file\">\n<span class=\"se-file-icon\"><strong class=\"se-blind\">첨부파일</strong></span>\n<div class=\"se-file-name-container\">\n<span class=\"se-file-name\">견적서 샘플 220922</span><span class=\"se-file-extension\">.xlsx</span>\n</div>\n<a class=\"se-file-save-button __se_link\" data-linktype=\"file\" href=\"https://download.blog.naver.com/open/61f47dcddd818559749bf3c6f71a621cbbea16f1de/EFsQb7dDxr3O9d9RLuoSggWaFwbSq-dpeF8XKG00xEFxTtTRU3sg7_e9DYRogyktqiSEUn6q4CQ-yRdHWrjbdIFfkp1FLwDC3Oh1ZwU/%EA%B2%AC%EC%A0%81%EC%84%9C%