e-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4590bea7-1138-4bfa-a7ca-a89bd4038ef0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-39fad6e5-3823-4bff-b5eb-984fd31589d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이트에서 주문을 받기 위한 양식 모음</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aa5ae180-d9a3-461c-81cf-77f19bbe2722\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ccbccab5-6ef0-4bc0-acda-56f707e0e371\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ef8bb69f-3f02-401b-8f23-553e627787c5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 외에 당신이 인쇄사이트를 개발한다면 필요한 문서가 뭐가 있을까요? 한번 저의 관점에서 모두 나열해 볼까요?</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9fd756f4-a298-4658-8e70-b40fff2a32b6\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4979a2bb-8442-4c48-98d7-2451e0c8d674\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-55979e12-91be-4746-808c-8f3b899deb48\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-902fab97-f29e-42b5-bfcd-a69c371547b8\" style=\"color:#444444;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-05a53ec3-5aa7-4fce-b9ac-ca3544bb9bb2\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f3b872a3-afee-462c-a5b3-59c00a96bbdd\" style=\"color:#444444;background-color:#ffffff;\">[사이트 준비를 위한 자료 모음]</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph